                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Williams</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-05-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 7, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have received 5 o’clock p.m. from admiral commanding the answer to my
                    communication of the 30th in regard to the American citizens captured on <hi
                        rend="italic">Competitor</hi>. He replies seventh article of the treaty 1795
                    and the protocol do not apply to them as they are not residents in accordance
                    with law relating to foreigners and they are to be tried by summary court
                    martial. I am preparing answer and protest in accordance with your telegram 2d
                    instant.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
